<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css' />
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.js" integrity="sha256-QWo7LDvxbWT2tbbQ97B53yJnYU3WhH/C8ycbRAkjPDc=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-OgVRvuATP1z7JjHLkuOU7Xw704+h835Lr+6QL9UvYjZE3Ipu6Tp75j7Bh/kR0JKI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/scriptEditorComentarios.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('navbar.ejs') %>
    <h1 class="m-5"><%= title %></h1>
    <div class="jumbotron mx-5">
      <div class="row mx-5">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col col-sm-3">
                    Museo:
                    <div class="form-group ml-3" style="border: black 1px solid;">
                        <select class="custom-select" id="museos">
                          
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-sm-3">
                    Sala:
                    <div class="form-group ml-3" style="border: black 1px solid;">
                        <select class="custom-select" id="salas" >
                          
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-sm-3">
                    Obra:
                    <div class="form-group ml-3" style="border: black 1px solid;">
                        <select class="custom-select" id="obras">
                          
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-sm-3">
                    <button class="btn btn-info mt-3" onclick="return buscarComentarios()">Buscar Comentarios</button>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="row ml-2 mt-3">
                <p>Info: Los comentarios cargan desde los actuales hasta los antiguos.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center m-5">
                <h4>
                   Resultados 
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5" id="mensajeError1" >
                <div class="alert alert-dismissible alert-danger">
                  <strong>No existen comentarios en la obra elegida o no existen obras/salas/museos.</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div className="col col-auto">
                    <table class="table table-hover table-responsive " style="width: 100%; height: 500px" id='tabla'>
                        <thead>
                            <th>Comentario</th>
                            <th>Accion</th>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody id="listaComentarios">
                 
                        </tbody>
                    </table> 
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btnCargar" onclick="return cargarC()">Cargar mas</button>
            </div>
            <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5" id="mensajeError2" >
                <div class="alert alert-dismissible alert-danger">
                  <strong>No hay mas comentarios en la obra elegida.</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="modal" id="modal-sesion">
      <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h5 class="modal-title">Sesi贸n Expirada</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
              <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <p>Su tiempo de sesi贸n expir贸. Vuelva a Iniciar Sesi贸n.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal">Aceptar</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>